security protections (lock screen, encryption, etc.).

We recommend that you:
  • Keep your Android device updated with the latest security patches.
  • Use a screen lock to prevent unauthorized access to your downloaded files.
  • Clear the in-app browser cache periodically if you use Private Mode.


8. DATA RETENTION

The App stores no data on external servers. Data retained on your device
(downloaded files, browser cache, download history) remains on your device
