will remove app-specific data, though media files saved to your gallery
folder ("InstaReelsDownloader") will remain on your device until you
delete them manually.


9. YOUR RIGHTS

Depending on your country or region, you may have the right to:
  • Access: know what data is collected about you.
  • Deletion: request deletion of your data.
  • Portability: receive a copy of your data.
  • Objection: object to how your data is used.

Since this App does not collect personal data on our servers, most of these
rights are exercised directly on your device:
  • To delete downloaded files: open the App's Files tab or your device gallery.
  • To clear browser data: use your device's App Settings → Clear Data.
  • To revoke permissions: go to Android Settings → Apps → [App Name] → Permissions.

